54:34.000 --> 54:37.000
That is, a subdued assessment is a manipulation,

54:37.000 --> 54:43.000
and, accordingly, a deliberately subdued assessment of a person's actions

54:44.000 --> 54:48.000
is also a deliberate manipulation of another person's consciousness.

54:49.000 --> 54:51.000
The next zone is the hidden zone.

54:52.000 --> 54:56.000
This is information about a person, known to him or herself,

54:57.000 --> 54:59.000
but hidden from the group for various reasons.

55:00.000 --> 55:01.000
