55:02.000 --> 55:05.000
it is just not possible to demonstrate one's knowledge,

55:05.000 --> 55:09.000
skills, skills, behavior patterns, behavior manners,

55:10.000 --> 55:15.000
or for some specific reason a person was even given the opportunity,

55:16.000 --> 55:18.000
but he did not want to demonstrate it.

55:19.000 --> 55:23.000
If in the previous case the so-called blind zone

55:24.000 --> 55:26.000
in order to get feedback,

55:27.000 --> 55:30.000
you need to ask more questions and ask,

55:31.000 --> 55:33.000
listen to the opinion of others,

55:33.000 --> 55:36.000
then in order to develop your hidden zone,

55:37.000 --> 55:39.000
you need to talk more,

55:40.000 --> 55:45.000
talk about yourself, demonstrate your qualities, skills, and skills without hesitation.

55:46.000 --> 55:50.000
And, accordingly, the fourth sector is the unknown zone.

55:51.000 --> 55:54.000
Otherwise, we say that this is our unconscious part,

55:55.000 --> 55:58.000
our Personality, which is not known to us,

55:59.000 --> 56:01.000
is not visible, is invisible to others.

56:01.000 --> 56:04.000
And this part of our Personality or our psychological institutions

56:05.000 --> 56:10.000
